{"tid":2016768,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[考評局又黃]歷史卷不只在於「日對中的利弊」，更在於「革命功成之後」","createTime":"2020-05-14T15:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T07:30:02.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"37c966720c3e609f4f5405e8fafbdc2622348fb1","tid":2016768,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"晚清到民國大批人先後留日=有人會潛移默化同流合污<br />\n借外國錢用礦抵押=有人會勾結外國勢力賣國求榮<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200514/_2020051419074352679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200514%2F_2020051419074352679.jpg&h=c9e78caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武昌一聲炮響，辛亥革命就為中國馬上帶嚟民主自由富強繁榮嗎？<br />\n冇<br />\n晚清新軍搖身成為各系軍閥<br />\n鄉願豪強變士紳議員<br />\n革命黨人加入瓜分<br />\n列強繼續扶持買辦軍閥瓜分土地資源<br />\n血汗工廠不斷開<br />\n（咁都唔明請睇讓子彈飛）<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2019/07/16/20190716-113043_U10931_M536229_dab4.jpg?itok=l_6gTqk6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2F20190716-113043_U10931_M536229_dab4.jpg%3Fitok%3Dl_6gTqk6&h=6d99a638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qqKCCAC3zOY/UrbZK28xfHI/AAAAAAAA9DQ/jBRRxNzp248/s1600/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-qqKCCAC3zOY%2FUrbZK28xfHI%2FAAAAAAAA9DQ%2FjBRRxNzp248%2Fs1600%2F4.jpg&h=8d372618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咩叫「光復香港」？<br />\n只係換旗換歌，唔係中國政府扶持執政就完嗎？<br />\n蘇東波倒台，內裏嘅官僚軍人，搖身成各種大亨，又或只係換個黨名繼續執政<br />\n今日嘅「保皇黨、建制派」當日又有幾多唔係港英嘅走狗？九七以後改換主人，又或者多個主人咁解<br />\n到時啲高官權貴，改頭換面咪又繼續壓榨⋯⋯<br />\n「地產霸權」呢幾年冇人再提起，只係而家變咗中外港各大巨頭瓜分，分贓不均而爭執<br />\n<br />\n光復香港以後，中環、金鐘嘅主人，係alex alan ada ronald joey amy<br />\n定仲仍然係鬼佬土豪加吸納精英？<br />\n<br />\n考評局唸得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca8592c7781def50874ce0b41cd12f1d12f55b6","tid":2016768,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"<em>魯迅《再談香港》：<br />\n<br />\n我實在有些愕然。真是人壽有限，&ldquo;世故&rdquo;無窮。我一向以為和人們搶飯碗要碰釘子，不要飯碗是無妨的。去年在廈門，才知道吃飯固難，不吃亦殊為&ldquo;學者&rdquo;所不悅，得了不守本分的批評。鬍鬚的形狀，有國粹和歐式之別，不易處置，我是早經明白的。今年到廣州，<span style=\"color: gold;\">才又知道雖顏色也難以自由</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有人在日報上警告我，叫我的鬍子不要變灰色，又不要變紅色。至於為人不可太瘦，則到香港才省悟，先前是夢裏也未曾想到的。<br />\n<br />\n的確，監督著同胞&ldquo;查關&rdquo;的一個西洋人，實在吃得很肥胖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港雖只一島，卻活畫著中國許多地方現在和將來的小照：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中央幾位洋主子，手下是若干頌德的&ldquo;高等華人&rdquo;和一夥作倀的奴氣同胞。此外即全是默默吃苦的&ldquo;土人&rdquo;，能耐的死在洋場上，耐不住的逃入深山中，苗瑤是我們的前輩。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n九月二十九之夜。海上</em>"},{"pid":"51315d735cf31de0202c30adece7d1eb3f100e90","tid":2016768,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-LtdhqHnpsJM/UYqh-ODKvbI/AAAAAAAAEFQ/UOcDa10S2CE/s1600/11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-LtdhqHnpsJM%2FUYqh-ODKvbI%2FAAAAAAAAEFQ%2FUOcDa10S2CE%2Fs1600%2F11.jpg&h=805fe771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8e2Ffg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8e2Ffg.png&h=edfa09ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[考評局好黃]方孝孺都考，建文、洪武、靖難，想影射咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000970</a>"},{"pid":"82bcefda7a88126e912eb2642d1e04cd8ba24119","tid":2016768,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"btw歷史都有5214人考（3個病咗）<br />\n點解網傳報導來來去去都係同一張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\